A minimalistic composition featuring a sleek, silver compression vice or clamp squeezing a translucent cube containing swirling streams of colorful data particles - blues, greens, and purples - being condensed into a much smaller, dense crystalline form on the other side. The background is clean white with subtle grid lines suggesting a technical blueprint. The compressed crystal on the right glows with concentrated energy, emitting small geometric fractals. The entire scene has a clean, modern aesthetic with sharp edges, subtle shadows, and a limited color palette of silver, white, and jewel-toned data streams. The perspective is slightly angled from above, creating depth while maintaining the minimalist feel.
